#  Flasks
 
Show
 Class "Life Flask" "Mana Flask" "Hybrid Flask"
 Rarity >= Normal
 SetTextColor 255 255 255
 SetBackgroundColor 131 234 28 200
 SetBorderColor 0 0 0 150 

Show
 BaseType "Diamond Flask" "Granite Flask" "Topaz Flask" "Sapphire Flask" "Ruby Flask" "Quicksilver Flask"
 Rarity >= Normal
 SetTextColor 255 255 255
 SetBackgroundColor 29 233 227 150
 SetBorderColor 0 0 0 150

